original_title: Britain’s Princess Anne meets Sri Lanka president
original_body_lines: ECONOMYNEXT – Britain’s Princess Anne, who is on a three-day official visit to Sri Lanka, and her spouse, Vice Admiral Sir Timothy Laurence, met with President Ranil Wickremesinghe.

The Princess Royal of the United Kingdom engaged in friendly conversation with Wickremesinghe and Professor Maithree Wickramasinghe, and marked the occasion by signing a guest commemorative book at the President’s House.
